JOIN projects ON projects.id = time_entries.project_id INNER JOIN users ON users.id = time_entries.user_id AND users.type IN ('User', 'AnonymousUser') LEFT OUTER JOIN enumerations ON enumerations.id = time_entries.activity_id AND enumerations.type IN ('TimeEntryActivity') LEFT OUTER JOIN issues ON issues.id = time_entries.issue_id LEFT OUTER JOIN custom_values AS cf_1 ON cf_1.customized_type = cf_1.id = (SELECT MAX(cf_1_2.id) FROM custom_values AS cf_1_2 WHERE cf_1_2.customized_type = cf_1.customized_type AND cf_1_2.customized_id = cf_1.customized_id AND cf_1_2.custom_field_id = cf_3.id = (SELECT MAX(cf_3_2.id) FROM custom_values AS cf_3_2 WHERE cf_3_2.customized_type = cf_3.customized_type AND cf_3_2.customized_id = cf_3.customized_id AND cf_3_2.custom_field_id = cf_3.custom_field_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN custom_values AS cf_7 ON cf_7.customized_type = 'Enumeration' AND cf_7.customized_id = enumerations.id AND cf_7.custom_field_id = 7 AND 1 = 1 AND cf_7.value <> '' AND cf_7.id = (SELECT MAX(cf_7_2.id) FROM custom_values AS cf_7_2 WHERE cf_7_2.customized_type = cf_7.customized_type AND cf_7_2.customized_id = cf_7.customized_id AND cf_7_2.custom_field_id =
